# E-Learning Platform Design System

## Overview
This design system is derived from analyzing 5 reference e-learning platforms (Skillshare, MasterClass, Duolingo, a course dashboard UI, and LearnXpert). Use these rules consistently across all components and pages.

---

## 1. Color Palette

### Primary Colors
```
--color-primary:        #1DB954;   /* Action green — CTAs, active states */
--color-primary-dark:   #158a3e;   /* Hover state for primary */
--color-accent-red:     #E53935;   /* Danger, alerts, highlight badges */
--color-accent-pink:    #D81B60;   /* Secondary accent, course card tints */
--color-accent-orange:  #E65100;   /* Warm category color */
--color-accent-purple:  #6A1B9A;   /* Category badge variant */
--color-accent-blue:    #0288D1;   /* Info, secondary category */
--color-accent-yellow:  #F9A825;   /* Stars, XP, streak indicators */
```

### Neutrals
```
--color-bg-primary:     #FFFFFF;   /* Main page background */
--color-bg-secondary:   #F5F5F5;   /* Section backgrounds, cards */
--color-bg-dark:        #121212;   /* Dark hero sections, video overlays */
--color-bg-dark-card:   #1E1E1E;   /* Dark mode cards */
--color-text-primary:   #1A1A1A;   /* Headings */
--color-text-secondary: #555555;   /* Body, descriptions */
--color-text-muted:     #999999;   /* Captions, metadata */
--color-text-inverse:   #FFFFFF;   /* Text on dark backgrounds */
--color-border:         #E0E0E0;   /* Dividers, card borders */
```

### Gamification / Status Colors
```
--color-streak:         #FF6D00;   /* Duolingo-style streak flame */
--color-xp:             #FFD600;   /* XP / points */
--color-league-bronze:  #CD7F32;
--color-league-silver:  #C0C0C0;
--color-league-gold:    #FFD700;
--color-progress:       #1DB954;   /* Progress bars */
--color-completed:      #43A047;
```

---

## 2. Typography

### Font Stack
```css
/* Display / Hero headings */
font-family: 'Sora', 'Nunito', sans-serif;

/* Body / UI text */
font-family: 'DM Sans', 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;

/* Monospace (code snippets) */
font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
```

### Type Scale
```
--text-xs:    11px / line-height: 1.4
--text-sm:    13px / line-height: 1.5
--text-base:  15px / line-height: 1.6
--text-md:    17px / line-height: 1.55
--text-lg:    20px / line-height: 1.4
--text-xl:    24px / line-height: 1.3
--text-2xl:   30px / line-height: 1.25
--text-3xl:   38px / line-height: 1.2
--text-4xl:   48px / line-height: 1.1
--text-hero:  60px / line-height: 1.05
```

### Font Weights
```
--font-regular:    400
--font-medium:     500
--font-semibold:   600
--font-bold:       700
--font-extrabold:  800
```

### Rules
- Hero / section titles: `font-extrabold`, `text-3xl` to `text-hero`, uppercase allowed for impact cards
- Course card titles: `font-bold`, `text-md` to `text-lg`
- Body / descriptions: `font-regular`, `text-base`, `color-text-secondary`
- Metadata (instructor name, duration, lesson count): `font-medium`, `text-sm`, `color-text-muted`
- CTA button labels: `font-semibold`, `text-sm` to `text-md`, uppercase or sentence case

---

## 3. Spacing System

Use an 8px base grid. All spacing values must be multiples of 4 or 8.

```
--space-1:   4px
--space-2:   8px
--space-3:   12px
--space-4:   16px
--space-5:   20px
--space-6:   24px
--space-8:   32px
--space-10:  40px
--space-12:  48px
--space-16:  64px
--space-20:  80px
--space-24:  96px
```

- Card internal padding: `--space-5` to `--space-6`
- Section vertical padding: `--space-16` to `--space-20`
- Navigation height: `56px` (compact) or `64px` (standard)
- Gap between course cards in grid: `--space-5` to `--space-6`

---

## 4. Layout & Grid

### Page Layout
```
Max content width:  1280px
Side padding:       clamp(16px, 4vw, 64px)
```

### Course Card Grids
```css
/* Default responsive grid */
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
gap: var(--space-5);
```

- Mobile (< 640px): 1 column
- Tablet (640–1024px): 2 columns
- Desktop (> 1024px): 3–4 columns

### Sidebar Layout (Dashboard / Course Player)
```
Sidebar width:       240px (collapsed: 64px)
Content area:        flex: 1
```

---

## 5. Components

### 5.1 Navigation Bar
- Background: `--color-bg-dark` (dark hero mode) OR `--color-bg-primary` with `border-bottom: 1px solid --color-border`
- Logo: left-aligned, `font-extrabold`, brand color or white on dark
- Nav links: `font-medium`, `text-sm`, `color-text-secondary`, hover → `color-text-primary`
- Search bar: pill shape (`border-radius: 9999px`), `background: --color-bg-secondary`, icon left
- Right side: notification bell icon + user avatar (circular, 32–36px)
- Active nav item: underline or background pill indicator

### 5.2 Course Card
```
border-radius:   10px
overflow:        hidden
background:      --color-bg-primary or colored (category-based)
box-shadow:      0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
transition:      transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease
hover:           translateY(-4px), box-shadow elevated
```

**Card structure (top → bottom):**
1. **Thumbnail** — 16:9 aspect ratio, object-fit: cover; may include overlay badges ("Staff Pick", "Original", "New")
2. **Category color bar** OR colored background (bold single color: orange, red, black, pink, purple, blue)
3. **Title** — `font-bold`, 2-line clamp
4. **Instructor name** — `text-sm`, `color-text-muted`
5. **Progress indicator** — thin bar (4px height), `--color-progress`, shown only if enrolled
6. **Lesson count / duration** — icon + text, `text-xs`, `color-text-muted`

**Badge overlays on thumbnail:**
```css
position: absolute;
top: 8px; left: 8px;
padding: 3px 8px;
border-radius: 4px;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 700;
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: 0.05em;
background: --color-accent-*;
color: white;
```

### 5.3 Buttons

**Primary CTA**
```css
background:       var(--color-primary);
color:            white;
padding:          10px 24px;
border-radius:    6px;
font-weight:      600;
font-size:        14px;
border:           none;
cursor:           pointer;
transition:       background 0.15s ease, transform 0.1s ease;
hover background: var(--color-primary-dark);
active transform: scale(0.97);
```

**Secondary / Outline**
```css
background:    transparent;
border:        2px solid var(--color-border);
color:         var(--color-text-primary);
border-radius: 6px;
padding:       9px 22px;
font-weight:   600;
hover border:  var(--color-text-primary);
```

**Ghost / Text Button**
```css
background:  transparent;
color:       var(--color-primary);
border:      none;
font-weight: 600;
hover:       underline or bg tint
```

**Icon Button (notification, bookmark)**
```css
width:         36px; height: 36px;
border-radius: 50%;
background:    transparent;
hover bg:      rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
display:       flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
```

### 5.4 Progress Bar
```css
height:        4px (thin) or 8px (prominent);
border-radius: 9999px;
background:    var(--color-border);      /* track */
fill:          var(--color-progress);   /* fill */
```

### 5.5 Avatar
```css
border-radius: 50%;
object-fit:    cover;
sizes:         24px (xs) | 32px (sm) | 40px (md) | 56px (lg) | 80px (xl)
border:        2px solid var(--color-border)  /* optional ring */
```

### 5.6 Accordion / Lesson List (Course Player)
```css
border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
padding:       14px 0;
```
- Collapsed: shows section title + chevron-down icon
- Expanded: shows lesson items with indent, play icon, duration
- Active lesson: `background: rgba(29,185,84,0.08)`, left border `3px solid --color-primary`
- Completed lesson: checkmark icon, title `text-decoration: line-through` optional OR muted color

### 5.7 Stat / Achievement Badge (Gamification)
```css
display:        flex;
align-items:    center;
gap:            var(--space-2);
padding:        8px 14px;
border-radius:  8px;
background:     var(--color-bg-secondary);
border:         1px solid var(--color-border);
```
- Icon: emoji or SVG, 20–24px
- Value: `font-bold`, `text-lg`
- Label: `font-regular`, `text-xs`, `color-text-muted`

### 5.8 Hero / Banner Section
- Dark or image-backed (`background-size: cover`, `overlay: linear-gradient`)
- Text: always white on dark backgrounds
- Max text width: `520px` for readability
- CTA button: `--color-primary` (green) on dark backgrounds for contrast

### 5.9 Section Heading
```
Title:    font-bold, text-2xl, color-text-primary
Subtitle: font-regular, text-sm, color-text-muted, margin-top: 4px
Divider:  4px wide, 32px tall left border OR underline accent in --color-primary
```

### 5.10 Tags / Pill Labels
```css
padding:       4px 10px;
border-radius: 9999px;
font-size:     12px;
font-weight:   600;
background:    tint of category color (10% opacity);
color:         category color (full);
```

---

## 6. Iconography

- Style: Outlined icons preferred (Lucide, Heroicons, or Phosphor)
- Size scale: `16px` (inline), `20px` (UI), `24px` (action), `32px` (feature)
- Color: inherit from text color OR `--color-primary` for active/highlighted icons
- Stroke width: `1.5px` to `2px`

---

## 7. Motion & Animation

```css
/* Standard transition */
transition: all 0.2s ease;

/* Card hover lift */
transform: translateY(-4px);
box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);

/* Button press */
transform: scale(0.97);

/* Accordion open */
transition: max-height 0.3s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;

/* Page load stagger (for card grids) */
animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease both;
animation-delay: calc(var(--card-index) * 0.06s);

@keyframes fadeInUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
```

**Rules:**
- Never animate more than 2 properties simultaneously (performance)
- `prefers-reduced-motion`: disable all transforms and fade durations → snap to final state
- Avoid looping animations on core UI elements (use only for loading states or illustrations)

---

## 8. Shadows

```
--shadow-xs:  0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)
--shadow-sm:  0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
--shadow-md:  0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)
--shadow-lg:  0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)
--shadow-xl:  0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.16)
```

- Cards (default): `--shadow-sm`
- Cards (hover): `--shadow-lg`
- Modals / dropdowns: `--shadow-xl`
- Navigation bar (scrolled): `--shadow-sm`

