## 9. Border Radius

```
--radius-sm:   4px   (badges, tags, small elements)
--radius-md:   8px   (cards, inputs, stat boxes)
--radius-lg:   12px  (modals, large cards)
--radius-xl:   16px  (hero sections, feature cards)
--radius-full: 9999px (pills, avatars, toggles)
```

